    <p>Article 6 - The Programs will have the following duration in months:</p>
    <p>Masters Program:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Minimum: twelve (12) months</li>
        <li>Maximum: thirty (30) months</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Doctoral Program:

    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Minimum  twenty four (24) months</li>
        <li>Maximum: fifty-four (54) months </li>
        <br>
        <li>§ 1 In the maximum duration of the Program is included the continuance or postponement period to which students are entitled. </li>
        <li>§ 2. Should there any difficulties arise in completing the thesis or dissertation in a timely manner, the deadlines established in accordance with this article for completing of the Program may exceptionally be extended for one (01) additional semester, as established in the Program’s Bylaws.</li>
    
    </ul>
    
    <p>Art. 7 This Resolution shall become effective on the date of its approval by this Board.</p>
    
